comment1.target=BorderedVariableSizeGameGrid(int,\ int)
comment1.text=\r\n\ Constructor\ for\ objects\ of\ class\ GameGrid\r\n\ \r\n\ @param\ width\ \ width\ to\ make\ the\ grid\r\n\ @param\ height\ height\ to\ make\ the\ grid\r\n
